headline: Marriott International Expands Presence in Coastal Xiamen with a Signed Agreement to Debut The Ritz-Carlton Brand
summary: Marriott International, Inc. today announced the signing of an agreement with Xiamen Green Development Investment Group to introduce The Ritz-Carlton to Xiamen Island in Fujian Province. The Ritz-Carlton, Xiamen will deliver its legendary service and elegant aesthetic to immerse guests in one of China's most coveted destinations.
